{"tid":2346221,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聶手足被控上水遊行踢警 蘇文隆判監4個月","createTime":"2020-12-30T06:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T11:19:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a05727bfed0883300476694baec104c7bf4577d0","tid":2346221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:04:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12527&d=%2BG0gz%2BKtHqwTrAvvvLwqSAoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=2f8fdd7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12527</a><br />\n<br />\n#粉嶺裁判法院第一庭 <br />\n#蘇文隆主任裁判官 <br />\n#20200105上水 #答辯<br />\n<br />\n聶<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n襲擊在正當執行職務之警務人員。<br />\n被控於2020年1月5日，在上水中心2樓樓梯踢向高級偵緝警員49515 。<br />\n<br />\n被告認罪‼️<br />\n（詳情稍後補回～）<br />\n<br />\n法庭以6個月作量刑起點，最後判處4個月即時監禁。<br />\n辯方律師即時表示會上訴刑期，申請上訴期間保釋，法庭批准。"},{"pid":"a1c34e820c418ca1f479749b168c47cf41c3c1c7","tid":2346221,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:05:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd8acce81ef80d8554748a7f11e0565e59098e45","tid":2346221,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:16:40.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"749b8a9ca4556492a03aae739e1e70b7026189ba","tid":2346221,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:17:36.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"713a406d461acdf9f75f2cf56668f11a20a0dc4e","tid":2346221,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T06:18:08.000Z","msg":"竟然批准保釋"},{"pid":"7b0af7cf3e317c9d38df110